  "2376580": {
    "name": "TRIBE NINE：战极死游",
    "steam_appid": 2376580,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376580/extras/44ca74ef20f337abcec3a200beee1532.avif?t=1744953823\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时值20XX年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事发生于被死亡游戏支配的近未来新东京。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了夺回失去的自由和梦想，少年少女们展开了与死亡相伴的残酷战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376580/extras/618d84a228148ed792b903c88a02c99e.poster.avif?t=1744953823\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376580/extras/618d84a228148ed792b903c88a02c99e.webm?t=1744953823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376580/extras/618d84a228148ed792b903c88a02c99e.mp4?t=1744953823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将操作角色一边在新东京各个特色鲜明的“城市”中冒险，一边击败阻挡前进道路的强敌，逐一解放城市。战斗队伍由三人组成，三人在战场上可同时战斗。队友们会根据战况采取行动，除了能吸引敌人的注意或进行回复，还能进行三人连携攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，每个角色都有着独特的个性，根据编队中角色的组合，战斗策略和攻略方法会千变万化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376580/extras/6d3a3e7b3730edfcd4011513d9c1f39e.poster.avif?t=1744953823\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376580/extras/6d3a3e7b3730edfcd4011513d9c1f39e.webm?t=1744953823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376580/extras/6d3a3e7b3730edfcd4011513d9c1f39e.mp4?t=1744953823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《TRIBE NINE》游戏中，玩家将实际操作角色进行城市冒险，推进剧情。途中不仅有紧张刺激的战斗，还有各种各样的事件发生。玩家可以从路边或宝箱中获取道具，完成谜题等小游戏，或者接受街上居民的委托，接连不断的任務将持续到来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376580/extras/d989b0904a941f0b9b59b95d8b814c34.poster.avif?t=1744953823\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376580/extras/d989b0904a941f0b9b59b95d8b814c34.webm?t=1744953823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376580/extras/d989b0904a941f0b9b59b95d8b814c34.mp4?t=1744953823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个可玩角色的个性方面更是精心设计，其性格和特点会反映在技能和动作上，因而让玩家在操控不同角色时能有不同的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了角色升级外，还可以通过分配属性点或装备搭配组合来享受高度自由的育成过程。广泛的育成攻略甚至可以将原本擅长回复的角色打造为攻击特化角色，尽情追求属于你自己的独特育成方式吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《TRIBE NINE》将通过更新追加主线剧情和城市。玩家可以在不断扩展的《TRIBE NINE》世界中，免费（部分道具付费）享受游戏的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
